{"tid":605234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（年經）比人工4成家用算唔算正常？","createTime":"2018-03-25T12:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T13:01:51.000Z","uid":9640,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4bba7348d9d63056d22b251b9d06b556ab1c70bd","tid":605234,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:57:15.000Z","msg":"小弟人工好撚低，扣埋強積金一萬都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講起派錢$4000，佢就話我比嘅家用根本唔夠<br />\n咁岩我都係比$4000家用嘅<br />\n<br />\n我：如果我搬出去住  ，一間屋既大數少左支出，但我就唔會比家用<br />\n<br />\n老豆就激到係咁屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆：乜你計到咁絕忤逆反骨冇人好似你咁仆街！你搬出去住都要照比咁多家用！養到你咁大比錢老豆老母洗天經地義！<br />\n<br />\n我：不如我依家即刻係個窗跳出去一了百了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老豆：跳啦！最好你就快啲跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今個月就黎出糧  諗緊應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打係咪通常都比晒成份糧做家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：公屋窮撚"},{"pid":"65d8eb70f3c8e2002f59e54603f1dfe7b4e5bf40","tid":605234,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5b202795efc44b55230d65c6986ed7ea5a3dd27","tid":605234,"uid":604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"斷絕關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d7d90aab247653d486ef612188351761dce608","tid":605234,"uid":36813,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:00:13.000Z","msg":"如果一個月搵廿萬<br />\n比四成仲話有錢慢慢搣姐<br />\n你搵得一萬唔夠都比四千<br />\n你老豆老母真係好仆街下<br />\n除非佢地車你返工放工 日煮三餐 洗用佢地全包就話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0569fc76fb60b3ea60c92e02d01427806f119f8c","tid":605234,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65d8eb70f3c8e2002f59e54603f1dfe7b4e5bf40","